Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.67,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining　夏の午後に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}通り雨　傘の下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing　濡れた頬に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:34.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そっと口づけた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:41.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あの季節にまだ焦がれている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:50.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何も手につかずに　上の空の日々
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:55.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:01.42,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}まだ足りなくて　まだ消えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:07.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}重ねた手のひらから幼さが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:19.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そんなフレーズに濡れてく雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:26.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ足りなくて　まだ言えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:32.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}数えた日の夢からさよならが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:35.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:46.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}触れられずにいれたら　笑えたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.67,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining  夏日的午后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.84,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雨来了又去  留我在伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.93,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing  沾湿的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:34.06,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}轻轻一吻  现了红霞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:41.94,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}四季更了又替  不变的是焦急的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:50.33,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我无心做任何事情  心中想的一直是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:55.29,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:01.42,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}还想再索取一点  还感觉隐隐若现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:07.76,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}十指相扣  掌心微热  是你青涩的炽烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.68,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.77,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:19.85,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一字一句沁我心  像身旁飘落的雨点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:26.07,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只想再索取一点  告别梗在了嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:32.24,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}细数曾经满怀憧憬追逐梦想的当年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.49,0:22:35.41,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:38.46,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:46.59,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果不能伸手触摸  是否还能保持笑脸?
