Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,勇斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,仓鼠!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候也养过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友送的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,小不点!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来给你爸爸看的?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.75,0:00:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他今天休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要打电话叫他过来?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道爸爸住哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要一个人走过去?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这一带车子多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐我担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.56,0:01:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.48,0:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我差不多下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟着他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,门没锁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰…了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边
