Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,7日 8日 9日 10…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸好像回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们吓他一跳吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是该生气 还是该表扬…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这蛋包饭怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 你做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.65,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候变得这么能干了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈知道你来这儿吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的是你做的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我开吃了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给我吃一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,略咸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你看你弄得到处都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,纸巾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不要边吃饭边说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 爸爸你又吃这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸可喜欢这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么老是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让我喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,还说让我别挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.18,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快放暑假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,广播体操!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不过也对…现在也还有这个选择就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不去 爸爸没有暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那你干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不工作的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,读点书…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不读书的时候呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…我基本都在读书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…那你还干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最近久违地去看了一场电影来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才听到什么声音了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不存在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你听 这不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪妖怪 妖怪妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是小不点!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,小不点?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,话说里边太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,原来你是带他来给我看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要养吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的 我不养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:09:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸你养
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸可养不了 工作太忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.13,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法养个活物的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 和你妈妈一起养吧 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说不准养
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而且爸爸养了它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能…经常来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…那我考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,橘…你怎么在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,勇斗 拿麦茶来 快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,…嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,橘?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那件T恤是干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不想穿也可以不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…好吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 衬衫呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,太惨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这洗衣机是用来洗我的衣服的…还是不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我去趟自助洗衣店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,勇斗 好好跟姐姐道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 不要什么事都往妖怪头上想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.05,0:12:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 小不点呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在呢 它在吃白菜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么橘会在我家?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,勇斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸喜欢看书吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说是喜欢崇文学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.88,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}注：这里说的应是「纯文学」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,崇文?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,今天这天气也能下雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿只是过云雨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你们来接我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给 伞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小心摔跤!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家有这样的伞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我自己的折叠伞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想更多地了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 青蛙!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有只青蛙! 青蛙!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 养仓鼠其实挺不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想更多地了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为 一切都在去看电影的那一天结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我为什么会紧张呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 店长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,店长店长 小不点还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.54,0:16:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前也养过仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都是三线鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家那只是冬白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,西田你懂得还真多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么疑问尽管来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,橘? 你说什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:54.97,Comment,,0,0,0,,说起来我家似乎还留着一些玩具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,店长!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这些碎菜叶拿给小不点吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦…谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我从前也养过仓鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有疑问尽管找我!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.08,Comment,,0,0,0,,对了 我家里可能还留着一些玩具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.45,Comment,,0,0,0,,不介意的话我就拿过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:27.34,Comment,,0,0,0,,刚才想到我好像还有个电热器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,聊什么呢? 小不点吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.03,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是那只仓鼠吗? 是叫小点不?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,店长 帮我拍一张小不点的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这仓鼠啊 一养就停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,久保姐 不是小点不 是小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,咦? 现在的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:42.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,小不点 小不点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正经历店长生涯中与店员沟通最多的时期?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要的并不是什么商务指导书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一只仓鼠足矣!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,结衣你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,之前对店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很难闻啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可看你今天和他聊得还挺多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,聊的时候我是用嘴呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…这并不能改变我被她接纳的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.22,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,…应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我感觉最近的自己很躁动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己并没有什么变化啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.89,0:19:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,客人点单 芝士焗饭加饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,店员室…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都去找店长了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 别再提什么仓鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还不快去干活!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,工作 工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,店长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,以后有关仓鼠的问题 请你都来找我解决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前也养过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,…好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 小不点需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我都记在这上面了
Comment: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:41.26,Comment,,0,0,0,,
